panels.description: Peak instance count. With date of peak. Grouped aws as "non-gcp total": top(sum(max(count) by workerType not "-gcp"))

targets.query: SELECT top(max, workerType,15) FROM (SELECT max("runningWorkers") FROM "six_month"."tc_web_exec" WHERE ("workerType" =~ /^b-linux-gcp/) AND $timeFilter  GROUP BY time(1w),  "workerType" fill(null))

SELECT top(max, workerType,15) FROM (SELECT max("runningWorkers") FROM "six_month"."tc_web_exec" WHERE ("workerType" =~ /^b-linux/ AND "workerType" !~ /^b-linux-gcp/) AND $timeFilter  GROUP BY time(1w), "workerType"  fill(null))

SELECT top(sum,3), sum AS "workerType" FROM (SELECT sum("max") FROM (SELECT max("runningWorkers") FROM "six_month"."tc_web_exec" WHERE ("workerType" =~ /^b-linu(x|x-aws)/ AND "workerType" !~ /b-linux-gcp/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "workerType", time($interval*2)  fill(linear)) GROUP BY time($interval*2) fill(linear))
